      <prop type="x-translation-ref">素冠.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>庶見素冠兮，棘人欒欒兮，勞心慱慱兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>If I could but see the white cap,
My toiled heart is worn with grief!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
