      <prop type="x-translation-ref">素冠.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>庶見素衣兮，我心傷悲兮，聊與子同歸兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>If I could but see the white lower dress! —
My heart is wounded with sadness!
I should be inclined to go and live with the wearer!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
